data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This is a very motivated seller, so let's make this home yours. This corner lot home has been given a fresh update to make it move-in ready and is a true gem, offering spacious bedrooms, open living areas and a convenient location. Step inside to discover a haven of comfort and style. Fresh paint, new carpet, bathroom updates and a top-of-the-line HVAC system (less than 3 years old!) contribute to a welcoming atmosphere that is move-in ready. One exceptional feature that sets this home apart is the handicap-accessible lift in the garage, offering accessibility for everyone. A privacy fence tastefully surrounds the backyard and patio, creating the perfect environment for entertaining or relaxing.
